s.desc:
Minimum flux density allowed by the filter, in Jy.
            This is an exclusive interval bound;
            i.e. min &lt; flux &le; max.

Maximum flux density allowed by the filter, in Jy.
            This is an inclusive interval bound;
            i.e. min &lt; flux &le; max.

Minimum angular distance from phase centre allowed by the
            filter, in degrees. This is an inclusive interval bound;
            i.e. inner &le; r &lt; outer.

Maximum angular distance from phase centre allowed by the
            filter, in degrees. This is an exclusive interval bound;
            i.e. inner &le; r &lt; outer.

Threshold flux density for the intersection of region
                    1 and 2, in Jy. Region 1 is less than the threshold;
                    Region 2 is greater than the threshold.
